<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>{% if title %}{{ title }} · {% endif %}{{ site.title }}</title>
  <meta name="description" content="{{ site.description }}" />
  <meta name="keywords" content="금융, 재테크, 증시, 투자 인사이트, 데일리 뉴스" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="{{ site.url }}" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nanum+Gothic:wght@400;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="{{ site.title }}" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="{{ site.description }}" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="{{ site.url }}" />
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="{{ site.title }}" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:site" content="@martin" />
  <style>
    :root {
      font-family: 'Nanum Gothic', 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f7f2;
      color: #0e1225;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: #f8f7f2;
    }
    .app-shell {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 36px clamp(16px, 3vw, 40px) 56px;
    }
    header {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .brand-group {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 3vw, 3rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .tagline {
      color: rgba(14,18,37,0.65);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }
    nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    nav a {
      color: #0e1225;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding-bottom: 4px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    }
    nav a:hover,
    nav a.active {
      border-color: #0e1225;
    }
    .hero,
    .hero-detail {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 26px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(14,18,37,0.08);
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(14,18,37,0.08);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .hero-card strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      color: #0e1225;
    }
    .hero-card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(14,18,37,0.7);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .hero-meta {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: rgba(14,18,37,0.65);
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .layout-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 2.4fr) minmax(260px, 1fr);
      gap: clamp(28px, 3vw, 36px);
    }
    main {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0;
    }
    .issue-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 26px;
      padding: 26px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(14,18,37,0.08);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 35px rgba(14,18,37,0.08);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }
    .issue-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 22px 48px rgba(14,18,37,0.12);
    }
    .issue-card-content {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .issue-card h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2vw, 1.95rem);
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    .issue-card p {
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: rgba(14,18,37,0.8);
    }
    .issue-meta,
    .issue-source {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: rgba(14,18,37,0.6);
    }
    .tags {
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:10px;
    }
    .tag {
      background: rgba(14,18,37,0.08);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #1a213b;
    }
    .ad-slot {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(14,18,37,0.08);
      padding: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(14,18,37,0.06);
    }
    aside section {
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }
    aside ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      color: rgba(14,18,37,0.75);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 60px;
      padding-top: 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(14,18,37,0.12);
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: rgba(14,18,37,0.6);
    }
    .privacy-links a {
      color: #565b67;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .calendar-preview {
      margin-top: 18px;
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: rgba(14,18,37,0.6);
    }
    .calendar-preview li {
      background: rgba(14,18,37,0.05);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 6px 10px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .layout-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      nav { justify-content: flex-start; }
      header { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
      main { order: 2; }
      aside { order: 1; }
    }
  </style>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "NewsMediaOrganization",
      "name": "{{ site.title }}",
      "url": "{{ site.url }}",
      "description": "{{ site.description }}",
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "{{ site.title }}"
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="app-shell">
    <header>
      <div class="brand-group">
        <h1>{{ site.title }}</h1>
        <p class="tagline">{{ site.description }}</p>
      </div>
      <nav aria-label="Quick links">
        <a href="{{ site.url }}" class="active">홈</a>
        <a href="mailto:martin@example.com">문의</a>
        <a href="{{ site.url }}/privacy">프라이버시</a>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <section class="hero" aria-label="Hero spotlight">
      <div class="hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-card">
          <strong>Daily insight</strong>
          <p>매일 오전 06:00 KST 최신 글로벌 금융 이슈 5개를 큐레이션해 전술적 관점으로 요약합니다.</p>
          <p class="hero-meta">기준: {{ today.now | readableDate }} · 업데이트 자동화</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-card">
          <strong>AdSense ready</strong>
          <p>본문 집중을 해치지 않는 사이드바/카드 광고 위치만 남겨두고 광고 콘텐츠는 분리합니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-card">
          <strong>Structured clarity</strong>
          <p>핵심 요약・시장 영향・투자자 체크리스트로 구성해 한눈에 흐름을 파악할 수 있습니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="layout-grid">
      <main role="main">
        {{ content | safe }}
      </main>
      <aside role="complementary">
        <div class="ad-slot" aria-label="AdSense slot">
          <p><strong>AdSense slot (300x250)</strong></p>
          <p>수익화와 콘텐츠 집중을 모두 고려한 위치입니다.</p>
        </div>
        <section aria-labelledby="why-updated">
          <h3 id="why-updated">Daily signal tracker</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>금리, 통화, 원자재, 실적, 정책별 흐름</li>
            <li>뉴스는 태그로 자동 분류</li>
            <li>Cloudflare Pages 빌드 로그 → Telegram 알림</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
        <section aria-labelledby="recent-dates">
          <h3 id="recent-dates">최근 업데이트</h3>
          <ul class="calendar-preview">
            <li>02-24 · 5건</li>
            <li>02-23 · 5건</li>
            <li>02-22 · 5건</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </aside>
    </div>
    <footer>
      <div>© {{ today.now | year }} {{ site.author }} · Cloudflare Pages · Eleventy</div>
      <div class="privacy-links">
        <a href="{{ site.url }}/privacy">Privacy</a>
        <a href="{{ site.url }}/disclaimer">Disclaimer</a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
